&lt;p&gt;Chefs Raul Jimenez and Ligui Karazawa brought their respective experience from El Celler de Can Roca and El Bulli to Sao Paulo, making CLOS Restaurante one of the hottest restaurants in town. In a contemporary room with impeccable design details, the gastro tapas menu won the &lt;strong&gt;2014 Best Spanish Restaurant award by Veja S&atilde;o Paulo &lt;/strong&gt;magazine. Smart casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book by contacting Close de Tapas by phone at +55 11 3045 2220&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The restaurant appreciates a 24-hour advance notice for cancelations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

